        "### Three Power Lines\n",
        "\n",
        "Now suppose there are three power lines at positions $a = 1$, $b = 6$, and $c = 8$. The total cost is:\n",
        "\n",
        "```{=html}\n",
        "<div style=\"text-align:center;\">\n",
        "<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n",
